Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Dr George Gallup (1901 - 1984)
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00yj99v
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 3 Oct 1997
So you think you know how most people feel? Meet Dr George Gallup, the man who transformed our views on what really constitutes public opinion.